  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Relaxing Spa</strong></p>
<p>The spa is incredibly relaxing and has four therapy saunas, steam room and whirlpool, emotional shower, aroma room and a wonderful relaxation area looking out onto the garden. If you want to treat yourself even more, book yourself a massage or beauty treatment (payable locally).</p>
<p><strong>Hotel facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Heated indoor pool</li>
<li>Massages &amp; beauty treat</li>
<li>Free pool towels</li>
<li>One day free rental of Fiat 500 per stay (pay only for fuel)</li>
<li>Free use of the hotel's bikes (subject to availability)</li>
<li>E-bikes available for hire (€20 a day, payable locally)<span style="text-decoration: underline;"></span></li>
<li>Free transfers to walking routes five times a week, with maps and walking itinerary</li>
<li>Walkers rucksack provided in rooms</li>
<li>Fitness room</li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Parking</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>]]></facilityDescription>
