  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Superior Rooms </strong>sleep up to three people (extra bed is a single sofa bed). They have a contemporary style with comfy furnishings.</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Rooms</strong> sleep up to three people (extra bed is a single sofa bed). These rooms have a balcony.</p>
<p><strong>Suites</strong> sleep up to four people (extra bed is a double sofa bed). They have a separate double bedroom and a living area with a double sofa bed (suitable for two children or one adult).</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Single Rooms</strong> are also available and have a balcony.</p>
<p>Please request twin or double beds at the time of booking.</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Shower stall</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Safe</li>
</ul>
<p>Cots are available on request for approx. €15 per day, payable locally. </p>
<p><strong>Local fees &amp; taxes</strong></p>
<p>A resort tax of approx. €3.40 per person per day is payable locally.</p>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>]]></roomsDescription>
